snippet.title: Holynn (홀린) - Hangover MV
snippet.description:
Holynn (홀린) - Hangover MV

Holynn (홀린) 3rd EP [OFF-SCREEN]


빛나는 순간만 골라 붙여놓은 화면 속 세상은, 늘 우리를 흔들어 놓습니다.

[OFF-SCREEN] 은 그 광택 뒤에 숨겨진, 가려져 있던 진짜의 삶을 바라보는 앨범입니다.
SNS라는 무대 밖에서 결국 우리 모두 비슷한 고민을 안고 살아가고 있다는 사실,
그리고 그걸 아는 것만으로도 서로 조금 덜 외롭기를 바라며 만들어진 기록입니다.

이 앨범이 누군가에게는
“나만 이런 게 아니구나”라는 짧은 안도,
혹은 조용히 등을 쓸어주는 손길처럼 닿길 바랍니다.



01 Lo-Fi

우리의 모든 순간을 명작으로 포장할 필요는 없어

Composed by Holynn, Mango
Lyrics by Holynn
Arranged by Mango

E.Piano by Mango
Synthesizer by Mango
Guitar by 추윤성
Bass by Mango
Drum by Mango
Percussion by Mango
Backing Vocals by Holynn
Sound FX by Mango

Recorded by Holynn
Edited by Mango, Holynn
Vocal Mixed by Holynn
Mixed by LENNON @_lnnnnnn_
Mastered by 권남우 @821 sound


02 Overthinker (Feat. Taeb2)

어쩌면 난 이 뒤에 뭐가 올지
정말 아무것도 알고 싶지 않은가봐

Composed by Holynn, Mango, Taeb2
Lyrics by Holynn, Taeb2
Arranged by Mango, Holynn

A.Piano by Mango
E.Piano by Mango
Synthesizer by Mango
String by Mango
Guitar by 추윤성
Bass by Mango, Holynn
Drum by Mango, Holynn
Percussion by Mango
Backing Vocals by Holynn
Sound FX by Mango, Holynn

Recorded by Holynn, Taeb2
Edited by Mango, Holynn
Mixed by LENNON @_lnnnnnn_
Mastered by 권남우 @821 sound


03 Losin’ My Breath

널 싫어해야 하는게 맞는데
지금 우리 몸은 너무 가까워

Composed by Holynn, Mango
Lyrics by Holynn
Arranged by Mango

E.Piano by Mango
Synthesizer by Mango
Bass by Mango
Drum by Mango
Percussion by Mango
Backing Vocals by Holynn
Sound FX by Mango

Recorded by Holynn
Edited by Mango, Holynn
Vocal Mixed by Holynn
Mixed by LENNON @_lnnnnnn_
Mastered by 권남우 @821 sound


04 Hangover (title*)

내가 요즘 울상인 이유는
그냥 숙취일 뿐이야

Composed by Holynn, Mango
Lyrics by Holynn
Arranged by Mango

A.Piano by Mango
E.Piano by Mango
Synthesizer by Mango
String by Mango
Guitar by 추윤성
Bass by Mango
Drum by Mango
Percussion by Mango
Backing Vocals by Holynn
Sound FX by Mango

Recorded by Holynn
Edited by Mango, Holynn
Vocal Mixed by Holynn
Mixed by LENNON @_lnnnnnn_
Mastered by 권남우 @821 sound


05 Marching Song

어떻게 바꾸려 해봐도 나는 결국 나더라
이대로 그냥 계속 걸어 나가자

Composed by Holynn, Mango
Lyrics by Holynn
Arranged by Mango

A.Piano by Mango
E.Piano by Mango
Synthesizer by Mango
String by Mango
Bass by Mango
Drum by Mango
Percussion by Mango
Backing Vocals by Holynn
Sound FX by Mango

Recorded by Holynn
Edited by Mango, Holynn
Vocal Mixed by Holynn
Mixed by LENNON @_lnnnnnn_
Mastered by 권남우 @821 sound


06 CHAT GPㅜ

나 같은 부족한 사람도
어딘가에선 꽤나 쓸모가 있다고 하던데

Composed by Holynn
Lyrics by Holynn
Arranged by Holynn

Synthesizer by Holynn
Bass by Holynn
Sound FX by Mango

Recorded by Holynn
Edited by Holynn
Mixed by Holynn
Mastered by 권남우 @821 sound


07 Hangover (KOR ver.)

Composed by Holynn, Mango
Lyrics by Holynn
Arranged by Mango

A.Piano by Mango
E.Piano by Mango
Synthesizer by Mango
Guitar by 추윤성
Bass by Mango
Drum by Mango
Percussion by Mango
Backing Vocals by Holynn
Sound FX by Mango

Recorded by Holynn
Edited by Mango, Holynn
Vocal Mixed by Holynn
Mixed by LENNON @_lnnnnnn_
Mastered by 권남우 @821 sound





[Credits]

Executive Producer UNDFND @official_undfnd
Producer TKO, Elapse

Marketing Planning TKO
Promotion & Marketing Jeonga Oh

A&R Seungyong Beag
Administration Director Byungwon Kang


Music Video Directed by WOONGBI KIM @oaktop_visual


Presented by UNDFND


#Holynn #홀린 #Hangover
